It's not very common that I review a business like DD, however this location is an exception to it because they have outstanding service. I have breakfast here almost everyday, and have had for over 1 year now, it's on my way to the office and they already know my order which is usually medium iced latte regular milk one Splenda + egg white flatbread veggie. I don't have to say anything, they already know it.  My point is, they always have a BIG smile and serve everything in less than 1 minute. I can always see they are very enthusiastic about exceeding customers expectations and these people know and understand the value time for others has.  I wish many other businesses (especially in that area!) took note of their good service and made it a model to follow.  Congratulations guys, you are THE BEST! Keep shining.
